ygData.subject: A few questions on double jeopardy lvls
ygData.msgSnippet: Well ive made it through my 2nd hell lvl (35)....now on to 36. I have died 6 times now in 36 and lost a bubble every time....it sux. Well im clear on that but
ygData.messageBody:
Well ive made it through my 2nd hell lvl
(35)....now on to 36. I have died 6 times now in 36 and lost
a bubble every time....it sux. Well im clear on
that but not clear on a few other things.<br><br>1. I
seem to not be connecting as much or hitting as hard.
examplei normally hit for 70-78 in this lvl i cant seem to
hit for more than 38 or so ...with the occasional hit
that im used to<br><br>2. mobs seem to be resisting
alot more<br><br>/shrug i dunno what the deal is
<br><br>im still fighting same mobs ....but it just seems so
much harder and easier to die <br><br>oh well any
suggestions or answer would be appreciated.
